---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="The Morristown Table Awards"
  description="The first annual celebration of Morristown's best independent restaurants — judged by residents, recognized on the Green."
>

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="hero-eyebrow">Coming 2027</p>
      <h1>The Morristown Table Awards</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">
        The first annual celebration of Morristown's best independent restaurants.
        Judged by residents. Recognized on the Green.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="page-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div style="max-width: 680px; margin: 0 auto;">

        <p style="font-size: var(--text-lg); line-height: var(--leading-loose); margin-bottom: var(--space-8);">
          Every town that takes its food seriously eventually arrives at a question: who's the best?
          The Morristown Table Awards are our attempt to answer that question honestly —
          with editorial rigor, resident input, and a ceremony that belongs to the town.
        </p>

        <hr class="divider" />

        <h2 style="font-size: var(--text-2xl); margin-bottom: var(--space-6);">Award Categories</h2>

        <div style="margin-bottom: var(--space-10);">
          <div style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: var(--space-5); margin-bottom: var(--space-8);">
            <span class="badge badge-gold-table" style="flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 4px;">Gold Table</span>
            <div>
              <h3 style="font-size: var(--text-xl); margin-bottom: var(--space-2);">The Gold Table Award</h3>
              <p style="color: var(--color-ink-light); line-height: var(--leading-normal);">
                The top honor. Given to the single restaurant that best represents what independent restaurant excellence looks like
                in Morristown. Eligible: independent and local group restaurants only. Judged 60% by community polling, 40% by editorial panel.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: var(--space-5); margin-bottom: var(--space-8);">
            <span class="badge badge-category" style="flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 4px;">Category</span>
            <div>
              <h3 style="font-size: var(--text-xl); margin-bottom: var(--space-2);">Category Awards</h3>
              <p style="color: var(--color-ink-light); line-height: var(--leading-normal);">
                Named awards for specific excellence: Best Pizza (The Wheel), Best Italian (The Press), Best BYOB, Best New Restaurant,
                and others. Regional chains may be eligible for Category Awards. Winners are named by the editorial panel
                after community nominations.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: var(--space-5); margin-bottom: var(--space-8);">
            <span class="badge badge-institution" style="flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 4px;">Institution</span>
            <div>
              <h3 style="font-size: var(--text-xl); margin-bottom: var(--space-2);">The Institution Award</h3>
              <p style="color: var(--color-ink-light); line-height: var(--leading-normal);">
                For restaurants that have become part of the fabric of Morristown — not just good, but essential.
                Eligibility: independently or locally owned, 15+ years of continuous operation. Editorial selection only.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <hr class="divider" />

        <h2 style="font-size: var(--text-2xl); margin-bottom: var(--space-6);">The Ceremony</h2>
        <p style="color: var(--color-ink-light); line-height: var(--leading-loose); margin-bottom: var(--space-5);">
          Table Night on the Green. The first annual awards ceremony will take place on the Morristown Green —
          tasting stations, live music, and the presentation of the awards in the heart of the town these restaurants feed.
        </p>
        <p style="color: var(--color-ink-light); line-height: var(--leading-loose);">
          Year 1 is a building year. We're establishing the profiles, the methodology, and the community signal.
          The first awards will be given in 2027, based on 2026 visits and community input. That gives every
          restaurant on this platform a fair runway.
        </p>

        <hr class="divider" />

        <h2 style="font-size: var(--text-2xl); margin-bottom: var(--space-4);">Our Methodology</h2>
        <p style="color: var(--color-ink-light); line-height: var(--leading-loose); margin-bottom: var(--space-5);">
          Every restaurant nominated for a Gold Table Award is visited multiple times by the editorial team before
          being considered. We pay for all meals. No restaurant can apply for or purchase eligibility.
          Community polling is conducted through verified Morristown resident channels.
        </p>
        <a href="/about#methodology" class="btn btn-outline btn-sm">Full methodology →</a>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
